				<td colspan="2"><hr /></td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Every time you "/pet hold" or hotkey your pet should not attack until told to do so by you.  However, after he is told to attack, he will then protect you as normal, so after every fight you must "/pet hold" again to keep him from attacking mobs you aggro.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
