			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Additionally... If your pet starts attacking a mob and you tell him to hold, he still has "agro" on that mob until you tell him to back off.
<br />

<br />
So if your pet is fighting Mob X, and you /pet hold and send him off on Mob Y, when Mob Y dies, your pet will shoot over to Mob X unless you issue another /pet hold or back off.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Lupo</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
